high_descs: Look down and turn around and walk towards the sink then turn left
pick up the knife that is on the counter
hold the knife and turn right then another right then walk forward then turn left towards the counter
Look at the floor
then turn left walk forward and turn right towards the stove
stand by the stove put knife on the stove in a pan
turn right then walk forward and then turn left towards the counter
pick up the apple slice from the counter
turn left with the apple slice in hand then walk forward and turn right
put the apple slices on the stove next to the knife
pick up the pan from the stove
turn left and walk straight caring the pan over to the counter
place the pan on the counter
anns.task_desc: To place the apple and knife in a pan on the counter

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter above the dishwasher.
Pick up the butter knife on the back of the counter.
Go to the counter to the right of the stove.
Slice the apple on the counter.
Go to the stove.
Set the butter knife down in the pan on the back left burner of the stove.
Go to the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up a piece of apple on the counter.
Move back to the left to the stove.
Put the apple slice in the pan with the butter knife.
Pick up the pan with the knife and apple in it.
Go to the counter above and to the right of the dishwasher.
Set the pan down on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with an apple slice and butter knife inside on the counter.

high_descs: Turn and go to the counter that is to the right of the dishwasher.
Pick up the knife that is on the shelf on the back of the counter between the bottle of lotion and the grey cup.
With the knife in hand turn and go to the counter to the right of the stove.
Slice the apple in three parts that is on the counter.
With the knife in hand turn and go to the stove.
Place the knife in the pan that is on the back left burner of the stove on the left side.
Turn and go to the counter that is to the right of the stove.
Pick up the back right slice of the apple.
With the apple slice in your hand go to the stove.
Place the apple slice in the pan on the back left burner to the right of the knife that is in the pan.
Pick up the pan that is on the back left burner with the knife and apple in it.
With the pan in hand turn and go to turn the counter to the right of the dishwasher.
Place the pan on the shelf behind the counter between the lotion and the grey cup.
anns.task_desc: Place a knife and apple slice in pan and place on counter.
